g-4 ">\r\n<div class="bs-docs-example">[list type="star" color="#6EAD18"]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet[/list_item]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet[/list_item]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet[/list_item]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet[/list_item]\r\n[/list]</div>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums">&#91;list type="check" color="#6B82A2" &#93;\r\n&#91;list_item&#93; ... &#91;/list_item&#93\r\n&#91;/list&#93;\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>Ordered lists</h3>\r\n<p>A list of items in which the order <em>does</em> explicitly matter.</p>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-lg-4">\r\n<div class="bs-docs-example">[list type="roman"]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet[/list_item]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet[/list_item]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet[/list_item]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet[/list_item]\r\n[/list]</div>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums">&#91;list type="roman"&#93;\r\n&#91;list_item&#93; ... &#91;/list_item&#93\r\n&#91;/list&#93;\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-lg-4">\r\n<div class="bs-docs-example">[list type="decimal"]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet[/list_item]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet[/list_item]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet[/list_item]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet[/list_item]\r\n[/list]</div>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums">&#91;list type="decimal"&#93;\r\n&#91;list_item&#93; ... &#91;/list_item&#93\r\n&#91;/list&#93;\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-lg-4">\r\n<div class="bs-docs-example">[list type="alpha"]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet[/list_item]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet[/list_item]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet[/list_item]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet[/list_item]\r\n[/list]</div>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums">&#91;list type="alpha"&#93;\r\n&#91;list_item&#93; ... &#91;/list_item&#93\r\n&#91;/list&#93;\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>Number Block</h3>\r\n<p>A list of items in which the order <em>does</em> explicitly matter.</p>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-lg-4">\r\n<div class="bs-docs-example">[list type="numblocks1"]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.[/list_item]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.[/list_item]\r\n[/list]</div>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums">&#91;list type="numblocks1"&#93;\r\n&#91;list_item&#93; ... &#91;/list_item&#93\r\n&#91;/list&#93;\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-lg-4">\r\n<div class="bs-docs-example">[list type="numblocks2"]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.[/list_item]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.[/list_item]\r\n[/list]</div>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums">&#91;list type="numblocks2"&#93;\r\n&#91;list_item&#93; ... &#91;/list_item&#93\r\n&#91;/list&#93;\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-lg-4">\r\n<div class="bs-docs-example">[list type="numblocks3"]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.[/list_item]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.[/list_item]\r\n[/list]</div>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums">&#91;list type="numblocks3"&#93;\r\n&#91;list_item&#93; ... &#91;/list_item&#93\r\n&#91;/list&#93;\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-lg-4 first">\r\n<div class="bs-docs-example">[list type="smallnumber1" ]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.[/list_item]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.[/list_item]\r\n[/list]</div>\r\n<pre class="prettyprint linenums">&#91;list type="smallnumber1"&#93;\r\n&#91;list_item&#93; ... &#91;/list_item&#93\r\n&#91;/list&#93;\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-lg-4">\r\n<div class="bs-docs-example">[list type="smallnumber2" ]\r\n[list_item]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.[/list_item]\r\n[list_i